Jean or John ELIAS, Appellant, v. John D. NA-GLE, as Com’r of Immigration, San Francisco, California, Appellee. No. 6846. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 17, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NJETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellant, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
